item.title: 【Singles (lossless)】ALAC - Gloria Estefan | If We Were Lovers (Con los Años que me Quedan English Version) [ALAC 16Bit/44.1kHz]
item.description:
Genre: Bolero

If We Were Lovers is the english language version of her hit song “Con los Años que me Quedan”, a french version was also recorded but never released.

This english version was released as a single in United States, United Kingdom, Canada, South Africa, Japan and all Europe. The song reached #40 in the U.K. and the latin version reached #1 in every Latin American country.
